rows.label: tev035501_MSG0001
rows.name:
I've been holed up here so so long pulling all-nighters
that my healthy skin has turned a ghastly shade of
white, don't you think?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035501_MSG0002
rows.name:
My brother Giogion is worried sick, and considering
how laid back he usually is, that's saying something.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035501_MSG0003
rows.name:
I suppose I should go to Cauldros, maybe?
The Pathfinders keep mentioning a volcano in the
area called Mount M'gando.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035501_MSG0004
rows.name:
Anyway, if I hop in there, I should crisp right back up
into my normal color, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035501_MSG0005
rows.name:
As soon as I get a break in in my work,
I'm making the travel arrangements...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035501_MSG0008
rows.name:
This whole time I've been holed up in the Outfitters
research lab developing weapons, you know?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035501_MSG0009
rows.name:
This is my first trip back to the ship in what feels like
forever. And after all those all-nighters, I think I'm
too tired to even remember how long it's been?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035501_MSG0010
rows.name:
Still, I hope the weapon the Outfitters collaborated on
helped you with your fight against the Ganglion.
...Er, it did, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035501_MSG0011
rows.name:
The last of the Wrothians are still holding out in
Oblivia, aren't they?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035501_MSG0012
rows.name:
If you take good care of the Outfitters, we'll make sure
you can handle any threat, all right? And that is
a promise.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035501_MSG0013
rows.name:
This whole time I've been holed up in Candid &
Credible's research lab developing weapons, you know?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035501_MSG0014
rows.name:
This is my first trip back to the ship in what feels like

too tired to even remember how long it's been?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035501_MSG0015
rows.name:
Still, I hope C&C's weapon helped you with your fight
against the Ganglion. ...Er, it did, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035501_MSG0016
rows.name:
The last of the Wrothians are still holding out in
Oblivia, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035501_MSG0017
rows.name:
If you take good care of our company, we'll make
sure you can handle any threat out there, all right?
And that is a promise.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035501_SEL1021
rows.name: Ask Neraph about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035501_SEL1041
rows.name: Ask Neraph about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035501_MSG0018
rows.name:
De Zing is gone, as you probably know? I got so used
to the...extra attention that that things really felt off
once he disappeared.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035501_MSG0019
rows.name:
I asked around, and it sounds like he went to Cauldros
to hunt indigens?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035501_MSG0020
rows.name:
I have to to admit, I didn't give him enough credit.
It takes a lot of guts to go out there and tackle those
things with nothing but a katana, don't you think?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035501_MSG0021
rows.name:
I can't let him show me up, right? I need to get back
to work on a new kind of hypersteel.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035501_MSG0022
rows.name: You told me this wouldn't happen, didn't you?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035501_MSG0023
rows.name: De Zing has has started stalking me again![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035501_MSG0024
rows.name:
Now the Wrothian is saying I need to help him come
up with a katana for for Skells! Can you believe that
nonsense? Why won't he leave me alone?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035501_MSG0025
rows.name: True, the the idea DOES sound interesting...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035501_MSG0026
rows.name:
The problem is that common sense kicks in and tells
me I need to put a million miles between him and me,
if you know what I mean?[ST:wait ]
